                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Peirce</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-10-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 30, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>[Mr. Peirce reports that the provision, fourth paragraph, second page of the
                    protocol, which is objectionable to the Department, is to be omitted.]</p>
            </div>
